---
---

<figure class="evidence-bundle" aria-labelledby="evidence-bundle-title evidence-bundle-caption">
  <div class="evidence-bundle__header">
    <p id="evidence-bundle-title">一次执行的最小证据链</p>
    <span>同一 runId 连接所有记录</span>
  </div>

  <div class="evidence-bundle__flow" role="list" aria-label="Evidence Bundle 数据流">
    <section class="evidence-bundle__node" role="listitem">
      <span>01 · BEFORE</span>
      <strong>Manifest</strong>
      <small>输入 Hash、配置快照、随机种子、依赖身份</small>
    </section>
    <span class="evidence-bundle__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
    <section class="evidence-bundle__node" role="listitem">
      <span>02 · DURING</span>
      <strong>Runner</strong>
      <small>验证、执行、捕获 stdout / stderr、记录副作用</small>
    </section>
    <span class="evidence-bundle__arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
    <section class="evidence-bundle__node" role="listitem">
      <span>03 · AFTER</span>
      <strong>Structured Result</strong>
      <small>Exit Code、状态、计数、错误分类、Artifact 清单</small>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="evidence-bundle__proofs">
    <section>
      <span>TRACE</span>
      <strong>步骤证据</strong>
      <small>每一步的开始、结束、输入摘要、结果与耗时</small>
    </section>
    <section>
      <span>LEDGER</span>
      <strong>副作用证据</strong>
      <small>计划执行、实际执行、验证结果与补偿状态</small>
    </section>
    <section>
      <span>ARTIFACT</span>
      <strong>输出证据</strong>
      <small>路径、大小、媒体类型、Hash 与可读取验证</small>
    </section>
    <section>
      <span>REPORT</span>
      <strong>结论分层</strong>
      <small>当前事实、由事实推导的结论、尚未验证的假设</small>
    </section>
  </div>

  <figcaption id="evidence-bundle-caption">
    Exit Code 只回答进程如何结束。Evidence Bundle 还要证明目标步骤确实执行、产物确实存在且可读取、外部副作用可以核对。
  </figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
  .evidence-bundle {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.85rem;
    margin-block: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-gray-5);
    border-radius: 0.875rem;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--sl-color-accent) 3%, var(--sl-color-bg));
  }

  .evidence-bundle__header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .evidence-bundle__header p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 750;
  }

  .evidence-bundle__header span,
  .evidence-bundle__node span,
  .evidence-bundle__proofs span {
    color: var(--sl-color-accent-high);
    font-family: var(--sl-font-mono);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    font-weight: 750;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  .evidence-bundle__flow {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto minmax(0, 1fr) auto minmax(0, 1fr);
    align-items: stretch;
    gap: 0.55rem;
  }

  .evidence-bundle__node,
  .evidence-bundle__proofs section {
    display: grid;
    align-content: start;
    gap: 0.28rem;
    min-width: 0;
    padding: 0.875rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--sl-color-gray-5);
    border-radius: 0.62rem;
    background: var(--sl-color-bg);
  }

  .evidence-bundle__node strong,
  .evidence-bundle__proofs strong { font-size: 0.9rem; }

  .evidence-bundle__node small,
  .evidence-bundle__proofs small,
  .evidence-bundle figcaption {
    color: var(--sl-color-gray-2);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .evidence-bundle__arrow {
    align-self: center;
    color: var(--sl-color-accent-high);
    font-size: 1.35rem;
    font-weight: 800;
  }

  .evidence-bundle__proofs {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 0.55rem;
  }

  .evidence-bundle figcaption {
    padding-top: 0.875rem;
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--sl-color-gray-5);
  }

  @media (max-width: 54rem) {
    .evidence-bundle__flow { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .evidence-bundle__arrow { justify-self: center; transform: rotate(90deg); }
    .evidence-bundle__proofs { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr)); }
  }

  @media (max-width: 34rem) {
    .evidence-bundle__header { display: grid; }
    .evidence-bundle__proofs { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
